        "**Reasoning**:\n",
        "I will create the `app.py` file with basic Streamlit configurations, including importing the library, setting the page title, layout, and an initial application title and header, using the `%%writefile` magic command as instructed.\n",
        "\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {
